<p>"BLAME!" creator Tsutomu Nihei new fantasy manga series title "Tower Dungeon" is on cover of the upcoming Monthly Comic Sirius issue 12/2023<br>
<br>
After killing the king & kidnapping the princess, an evil sorcerer hides in a huge tower-like structure where strong magical beasts roam. A young farmer joins the rescue squad trying to save the princess by venturing into this enormous tower which once fell from the sky.</p>
